  "text": "Note that the condition of the theorem is independent of the choice of ball X, although the constant κ may change. The fact that we only get bounds for the lower box dimension of F C should not come as a surprise and one should not expect to be able to improve these bounds in general, see [CITATION_1] . Note that if, in the setting of Theorem 2.3, the box dimension of C exists, then so does the box dimension of F C .",
